# Title: SQLite Firefox Profile Data DB Access
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-04-08
# Level: high
# Description: Detect usage of the "sqlite" binary to query databases in Firefox and other Gecko-based browsers for potential data stealing.
# MITRE Tactic: Credential Access
# Tags: attack.credential-access, attack.t1539, attack.collection, attack.t1005
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_sqlite_firefox_gecko_profile_data.yml

CommandLine IN ("*cookies.sqlite*", "*places.sqlite*") Product="SQLite" OR Image IN ("*\\sqlite.exe", "*\\sqlite3.exe")